IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. HLLOWRLD.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01  VAR PIC 9(1).
01  S-3-VAR PIC 9(1).
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
0000-MAIN SECTION.
MOVE 1 TO VAR.
MOVE 1 TO S-3-VAR.
DISPLAY 'START'.
PERFORM 2-S
DISPLAY 'MIDDLE'.
MOVE 0 TO S-3-VAR.
GO TO 3-S.
DISPLAY 'END'.
GOBACK.
2-S SECTION.
DISPLAY '2-S'.
PERFORM 2-EXIT.
DISPLAY '2-S-END'.
2-EXIT.
DISPLAY '2-EXIT'.
IF VAR EQUAL TO 1 THEN
PERFORM 3-S
END-IF.
DISPLAY '2-EXIT-END'.
3-S SECTION.
DISPLAY '3-S'.
MOVE 0 TO VAR.
IF S-3-VAR EQUAL TO 1 THEN
GO TO 2-EXIT
END-IF.